# Keep the Docker build context lean (the deploy/nocix image only needs go.mod + cmd/ + internal/).
# The Dockerfile COPYs sources selectively, so this mainly trims what's SENT to the daemon and
# guarantees build-irrelevant / local-only files never enter a build.
.git/
*.exe
/dist/
config.json            # the LIVE gitignored rig config — must never enter an image
*.log
.playwright-cli/
experiments/
docs/
web/
README.md
